t/status/1596931031055171584?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 27, 2022</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>而在不同帖文下的评论区，都有网友金句被顶至热门：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/11/image-1669629152933.png\" alt=\"file\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/11/image-1669629183539.png\" alt=\"file\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/11/image-1669629225408.png\" alt=\"file\" /></p>\n<p>同时，也有网友发现，<a href=\"https://weibo.com/u/7286955267\" title=\"赵立坚\">赵立坚</a>的个人微博尚未开启“精选评论”，也暂未对网民的评论进行清理，这让赵立坚微博评论区成为了一个新的反对言论集结地。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/11/image-1669629628235.png\" alt=\"filev\" /></p>\n","author":1069,"categories":[45870,41492,45445,43134,45392,45440],"tags":[22015,39979,40280,44678,45196,46229,46230]}